## Third-Party Assets Notice

This software includes third-party assets that may be subject to separate licenses:

### Audio Files
Some audio files in the `GameEngine/Sounds/` directory may be copyrighted material.
For legal distribution, these files should be replaced with royalty-free alternatives
or properly licensed content.

### 3D Models and Textures
The 3D models and textures included in this project may have separate licensing terms.
Please verify the licensing status of any assets before redistribution.

### Dependencies
This project uses the following open-source libraries:
- GLFW (zlib/libpng license)
- GLEW (Modified BSD License, MIT License, and others)
- GLM (MIT License or The Happy Bunny License)
- OpenAL Soft (LGPL)
- Assimp (3-clause BSD license)

See the respective library documentation for detailed licensing information.
